Zhang He, May 12, project: netpong 
hxzhang1@ualr.edu 

1. compile: 
    make 

2. implement:
  2.1 start server 
    ./net_main port 
    example: ./net_main 3002
  2.2 start client
    ./net_main hostname port 
    example: ./net_main davidz-T430 3002
  2.3 client serve the ball
    press 'j' and 'k' move the paddle, and
    press 's' or 'S' to serve the ball
  2.4 it works following the steps in the report, when it finishes, the result will be shown in the terminal  
  2.5 press 'Q' to quit the game at anytime 


  





